graph TD
    subgraph "Module Room"
        A[Room Aggregate]
        A -->|state change| E1[RoomStateChanged]
        A -->|rename| E2[RoomRenamedEvent]
        A -->|relocate| E3[RoomRelocatedEvent]
        A -->|capacity change| E4[RoomCapacityChanged]
    end

    subgraph "Module Workshop"
        B{Workshop State?}

        E1 & E2 & E3 & E4 --> B

        B -->|DRAFT| D[No action<br>No room reference]
        B -->|PUBLISHED| G[Process PUBLISHED Reactions]

        B -->|SCHEDULED| F[Process SCHEDULED Reactions]

        %% SCHEDULED
        F --> F_T{Event type?}
        F_T -->|Renamed| F1[Update room_name_snapshot]
        F_T -->|Relocated| F2[Update room_location_snapshot]
        F_T -->|CapacityChanged| F3[Update room_capacity_snapshot]
        F_T -->|StateChanged → MAINTENANCE| F4[hasRoomWarning = true<br>Keep SCHEDULED]
        F_T -->|StateChanged → ACTIVE| F5[hasRoomWarning = false<br>Keep SCHEDULED]
        F_T -->|StateChanged → DEACTIVATED| F6[returnToDraft()<br>SCHEDULED → DRAFT]

        %% PUBLISHED
        G --> G_T{Event type?}
        G_T -->|Renamed| G1[Update snapshot<br>Notify registrations]
        G_T -->|Relocated| G2[Update snapshot<br>Insert event<br>Notify registrations]
        G_T -->|CapacityChanged| G3{Delta check}
        G3 -->|Within limit| G3a[Update capacity silently]
        G3 -->|Exceeded| G3b[OVER_CAPACITY_PENDING<br>Admin notification]
        G_T -->|StateChanged → MAINTENANCE| G4[ROOM_DEACTIVATED_PENDING<br>Admin notification]
        G_T -->|StateChanged → DEACTIVATED| G5[ROOM_DEACTIVATED_PENDING<br>Urgent admin<br>Registration impact]
    end

    style F4 fill:#fff3cd
    style F5 fill:#d4edda
    style F6 fill:#f8d7da
    style G4 fill:#f8d7da
    style G5 fill:#f8d7da
    style G3b fill:#f8d7da
